<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
  <title>Privacy Policy | GetPawsy</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
  <style>
    .legal-page { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; }
    .legal-page h1 { color: var(--pawsy-primary, #6366f1); margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .legal-page .last-updated { color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 30px; }
    .legal-page h2 { color: #333; margin: 30px 0 15px; border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0; padding-bottom: 10px; }
    .legal-page p, .legal-page li { line-height: 1.8; color: #444; }
    .legal-page ul { padding-left: 25px; margin: 15px 0; }
    .legal-page .highlight { background: #f8f9ff; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; border-left: 4px solid var(--pawsy-primary, #6366f1); margin: 20px 0; }
    .legal-page table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0; }
    .legal-page th, .legal-page td { border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; padding: 12px; text-align: left; }
    .legal-page th { background: #f8f9ff; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('../partials/header') %>

  <main class="legal-page">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: December 2024</p>

    <div class="highlight">
      <p><strong>Your Privacy Matters.</strong> This Privacy Policy explains how GetPawsy collects, uses, shares, and protects your personal information. We comply with CCPA (California) and GDPR (European) requirements.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <h3>Personal Information</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Account Data:</strong> Name, email address, password, phone number</li>
      <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> Credit card details, billing address (processed securely)</li>
      <li><strong>Shipping Information:</strong> Delivery address, contact details</li>
      <li><strong>Order History:</strong> Products purchased, order dates, transaction amounts</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Automatically Collected Information</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Browser type, operating system, device identifiers</li>
      <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Pages visited, time spent, click patterns</li>
      <li><strong>Location Data:</strong> General geographic location based on IP address</li>
      <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> See our <a href="/legal/cookies">Cookie Policy</a></li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <table>
      <tr>
        <th>Purpose</th>
        <th>Legal Basis</th>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Process orders and payments</td>
        <td>Contract performance</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Send order confirmations and updates</td>
        <td>Contract performance</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Provide customer support</td>
        <td>Legitimate interest</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Personalize recommendations (AI)</td>
        <td>Consent / Legitimate interest</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Prevent fraud</td>
        <td>Legal obligation / Legitimate interest</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Marketing communications</td>
        <td>Consent</td>
      </tr>
    </table>

    <h2>3. AI and Automated Processing</h2>
    <p>GetPawsy uses artificial intelligence for:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Product Recommendations:</strong> AI analyzes your browsing and purchase history to suggest relevant products</li>
      <li><strong>Pawsy Chatbot:</strong> AI-powered customer support that processes your messages</li>
      <li><strong>Pricing Engine:</strong> Dynamic pricing based on market conditions</li>
      <li><strong>Returns Assessment:</strong> AI evaluates return requests for processing</li>
      <li><strong>Fraud Detection:</strong> Automated systems to protect against fraudulent activity</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You have the right to request human review of automated decisions. See our <a href="/legal/ai">AI Disclosure</a> for more details.</p>

    <h2>4. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
    <p>We use cookies and similar technologies for:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Essential website functionality</li>
      <li>Analytics and performance monitoring</li>
      <li>Personalization and recommendations</li>
      <li>Marketing and advertising</li>
    </ul>
    <p>For detailed information, please see our <a href="/legal/cookies">Cookie Policy</a>.</p>

    <h2>5. Third-Party Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We may share your information with:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Payment Processors:</strong> Stripe, PayPal for secure transactions</li>
      <li><strong>Shipping Partners:</strong> USPS, UPS, FedEx for order delivery</li>
      <li><strong>Cloud Services:</strong> For data storage and processing</li>
      <li><strong>Analytics Providers:</strong> To understand website usage</li>
      <li><strong>AI Service Providers:</strong> OpenAI for chatbot and recommendations</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</p>

    <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
    <h3>CCPA Rights (California Residents)</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Right to know what personal information is collected</li>
      <li>Right to delete personal information</li>
      <li>Right to opt-out of sale of personal information</li>
      <li>Right to non-discrimination for exercising rights</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>GDPR Rights (EU/EEA Residents)</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Right to access your data</li>
      <li>Right to rectification</li>
      <li>Right to erasure ("right to be forgotten")</li>
      <li>Right to restrict processing</li>
      <li>Right to data portability</li>
      <li>Right to object to processing</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>7. Opt-Out Instructions</h2>
    <p>To exercise your privacy rights:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Email Opt-Out:</strong> Click "unsubscribe" in any marketing email</li>
      <li><strong>Cookie Preferences:</strong> Manage via our cookie banner or browser settings</li>
      <li><strong>Account Deletion:</strong> Contact us at privacy@getpawsy.com</li>
      <li><strong>Data Request:</strong> Email privacy@getpawsy.com with your request</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>8. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We retain your data for:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Account information: Until account deletion + 30 days</li>
      <li>Order history: 7 years (legal requirements)</li>
      <li>Marketing preferences: Until you unsubscribe</li>
      <li>Chat history: 1 year</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>9. Data Security</h2>
    <p>We implement industry-standard security measures including:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>SSL/TLS encryption for data transmission</li>
      <li>Secure payment processing (PCI-DSS compliant)</li>
      <li>Regular security audits</li>
      <li>Access controls and authentication</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>10. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>GetPawsy is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children. If you believe we have collected information from a child, please contact us immediately.</p>

    <h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>For privacy-related inquiries:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Email: privacy@getpawsy.com</li>
      <li>Website: <a href="/contact">Contact Page</a></li>
    </ul>
  </main>

  <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
